data.title: Patrick Joseph O'Sullivan
data.meta_description:
Plaque on the wall of Wembley Stadium that reads;
	
	In loving memory of
	Patrick Joseph O' Sullivan
	Who tragically died in the construction of Wembley Stadium on 15th. January 2004.
	Aged 54 years
	
	"Every action of our lives touches on some chord that will vibrate in eternity"
